                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 513.) I saw the prisoner take this handkerchief from the prosecutor's pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I saw it throwing about, and picked it up under the gentleman's feet; the policeman laid hold of me; I had not been a minute off the water, where I work.</p>
